cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "OpenClaw-Agent: A Risk-Aware LLM-Assisted Trading Agent for Secure Financial AI"
abstract: "OpenClaw-Agent is a risk-aware, LLM-assisted paper-trading agent built on the Alpaca paper-trading API. It combines deterministic technical signals (EMA crossover, RSI, momentum) with an optional LLM review-only filter and an explicit risk envelope (per-position cap, gross exposure, stop-loss, take-profit). Developed as a PGE5 AI-in-Finance term paper at Aivancity, inspired by the SecureFinAI Contest 2026 (Task V, OpenClaw / Alpaca)."
authors:
